to distinguish between these two:

```
      BaseException(const BaseException &e);
      template <typename... Types>
      BaseException(Types const &... types);
```

I think there is an easier way to accomplish this.

Modify `MTimeComparator`:

```python

def __init__(self, filenames, compare_func=None):
    self.compare_func = compare_func or os.path.getmtime
```

Then you could implement the rest of this change outside of this repo:

```python

def build_logging_mtime_comparator(err_logger):
    def func(filenames):
        return MTimeComparator(filenames, compare_func=try_getmtime_else_log)
   
    return func

